OL,4,CCovid in Wales: Care home visiting
OL,5,Crestrictions eased
OL,6, Many families and friends will be able
OL,7, to visit loved ones inside care homes
OL,8, in Wales and hold their hand for the
OL,9, first time in over a year.
OL,11,FUntil now only two designated visitors
OL,12,Fcould make visits indoors, due to
OL,13,Fguidance set by the Welsh government.
OL,15,FFrom Monday, changes in guidance allow
OL,16,Fanyone to visit, but residents can only
OL,17,Fsee two people at a time.
OL,19,FHowever it is down to individual care
OL,20,Fhomes and local authorities to decide
OL,21,Fwhether to allow visits.
